---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="MajiMap"
  description="MajiMap is an interactive water data platform mapping water pricing, quality, and access across Nairobi and East Africa. Making water inequality visible, measurable, and actionable."
>
  <section class="page-hero">
    <div class="hero-badge"><span class="pulse"></span> Coming Soon</div>
    <h1>Maji<em>Map</em></h1>
    <p>An interactive, public water data platform that makes water access, pricing, and quality visible across Nairobi and East Africa.</p>
    <svg class="hero-wave" viewBox="0 0 1440 100" preserveAspectRatio="none">
      <path d="M0,60 C360,100 720,20 1080,60 C1260,80 1380,50 1440,60 L1440,100 L0,100Z" fill="white"/>
    </svg>
  </section>

  <!-- What is MajiMap -->
  <section>
    <div class="section-inner">
      <div class="section-label">The Concept</div>
      <div class="section-title">Making Water Inequality Visible</div>
      <div class="section-subtitle">MajiMap turns invisible inequality into undeniable evidence — a crowd-sourced and platform-verified data layer for water across East Africa.</div>

      <div class="concept-callout fade-in">
        <h3>"Why does water cost 10x more in Kibera than in Karen?"</h3>
        <p>MajiMap answers this question with data. It is MiMaji Foundation's flagship data product — the tool that transforms assumptions into actionable, shareable evidence.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="layers-grid fade-in">
        <div class="layer-card">
          <div class="layer-num">01</div>
          <div class="layer-icon">💰</div>
          <h3>Water Pricing</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>Average price per litre by estate and neighbourhood</li>
            <li>Price comparison: informal vendor vs. utility vs. bottled vs. <a href="https://mimaji.co.ke" target="_blank" rel="noopener">MiMaji platform</a></li>
            <li>Price inequality index across income levels</li>
            <li>Historical price trends as data accumulates</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="layer-card">
          <div class="layer-num">02</div>
          <div class="layer-icon">🔬</div>
          <h3>Water Quality</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>TDS readings by location from Foundation testing events</li>
            <li>Bacteriological test results where available</li>
            <li>Quality rating: Safe / Caution / Unsafe (green/amber/red)</li>
            <li>Source type: borehole, piped, vendor, rainwater</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="layer-card">
          <div class="layer-num">03</div>
          <div class="layer-icon">📍</div>
          <h3>Access & Coverage</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>Coverage gaps — areas with no reliable clean water</li>
            <li>Vendor and access point locations</li>
            <li>Average distance to nearest clean water source</li>
            <li>Time-to-water estimates for residents</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="layer-card">
          <div class="layer-num">04</div>
          <div class="layer-icon">📱</div>
          <h3>MiMaji Integration</h3>
          <ul>
            <li><a href="https://mimaji.co.ke" target="_blank" rel="noopener">MiMaji</a> delivery coverage zones</li>
            <li>Verified vendor locations on the platform</li>
            <li>Real-time pricing from platform data</li>
            <li>"Order water now" for covered areas</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Why It Matters -->
  <section class="bg-sand">
    <div class="section-inner">
      <div class="section-label">Why It Matters</div>
      <div class="section-title">Data That Drives Change</div>

      <div class="matters-grid fade-in">
        <div class="matters-card">
          <h4>For Donors & Grant Funders</h4>
          <p>MajiMap provides the baseline data and measurable outcomes that institutional funders require. It proves MiMaji Foundation is building infrastructure, not just running events.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="matters-card">
          <h4>For Advocacy & Policy</h4>
          <p>When water pricing inequality is public, visualised, and shareable, it becomes a tool for holding utilities and governments accountable. MajiMap makes this impossible to ignore.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="matters-card">
          <h4>For Communities</h4>
          <p>Residents discover their water quality data, see the price gap, and find better alternatives — including verified water delivery through the <a href="https://mimaji.co.ke" target="_blank" rel="noopener">MiMaji platform</a>.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="matters-card">
          <h4>For Media</h4>
          <p>Data-driven inequality stories go viral. A MajiMap visual showing the price gap across Nairobi is the kind of content Nation Africa, The Guardian, and Al Jazeera publish.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Roadmap -->
  <section>
    <div class="section-inner">
      <div class="section-label">Roadmap</div>
      <div class="section-title">Building MajiMap Step by Step</div>

      <div class="roadmap fade-in">
        <div class="roadmap-item active">
          <div class="roadmap-marker"></div>
          <div class="roadmap-content">
            <div class="roadmap-phase">Phase 1 — Now</div>
            <h4>Static Data Visualisation</h4>
            <p>Using existing Nairobi Water Price Map research to build the first interactive visualisation. Colour-coded estate map with price overlays and shareable social media assets.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="roadmap-item">
          <div class="roadmap-marker"></div>
          <div class="roadmap-content">
            <div class="roadmap-phase">Phase 2</div>
            <h4>Water Quality Data Layer</h4>
            <p>Community water quality testing events across target estates. TDS and bacteriological testing with green/amber/red quality ratings added to the map.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="roadmap-item">
          <div class="roadmap-marker"></div>
          <div class="roadmap-content">
            <div class="roadmap-phase">Phase 3</div>
            <h4>Interactive Platform</h4>
            <p>Searchable, zoomable map interface. Community submission feature for residents to report local water data. Integration with MiMaji platform vendor data for real-time pricing.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="roadmap-item">
          <div class="roadmap-marker"></div>
          <div class="roadmap-content">
            <div class="roadmap-phase">Phase 4</div>
            <h4>East Africa Expansion</h4>
            <p>Expand to Kampala, Dar es Salaam, Addis Ababa, Kigali, Bujumbura, and Mogadishu. Position MajiMap as the definitive public water data source for East Africa.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="cta-section">
    <div class="section-title">Help Us Build MajiMap</div>
    <p>MajiMap needs data partners, funding, and community contributors. Whether you're a researcher, donor, or local resident — your contribution shapes the map.</p>
    <div class="cta-buttons">
      <a href="/contact/" class="btn btn-white">Get Involved &rarr;</a>
      <a href="/take-action/" class="btn btn-outline">Support Our Work</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .pulse {
    width: 8px;
    height: 8px;
    background: var(--gold);
    border-radius: 50%;
    display: inline-block;
    animation: pulse 2s infinite;
  }

  .concept-callout {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--blue-deep), var(--blue));
    border-radius: 20px;
    padding: 3rem;
    text-align: center;
    color: var(--white);
    margin-top: 3rem;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .concept-callout h3 {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-size: 1.6rem;
    color: var(--gold);
    font-style: italic;
    margin-bottom: 0.8rem;
  }

  .concept-callout p {
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
    max-width: 600px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .layers-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: 2rem;
  }

  .layer-card {
    padding: 2.2rem;
    border-radius: 16px;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    background: var(--white);
    transition: all 0.3s;
    position: relative;
  }

  .layer-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-4px);
    box-shadow: 0 12px 40px rgba(10, 94, 181, 0.1);
  }

  .layer-num {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-size: 2rem;
    color: var(--blue);
    opacity: 0.2;
    position: absolute;
    top: 1.5rem;
    right: 1.5rem;
  }

  .layer-icon {
    font-size: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.8rem;
  }

  .layer-card h3 {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    color: var(--blue-deep);
    margin-bottom: 0.8rem;
  }

  .layer-card ul {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
  }

  .layer-card ul li {
    font-size: 0.82rem;
    color: var(--text-light);
    padding: 0.35rem 0;
    padding-left: 1.2rem;
    position: relative;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  .layer-card ul li::before {
    content: '→';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: var(--teal);
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .layer-card a {
    color: var(--blue);
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .matters-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: 1.5rem;
    margin-top: 3rem;
  }

  .matters-card {
    padding: 2rem;
    border-radius: 14px;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    background: var(--white);
    transition: all 0.3s;
  }

  .matters-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(10, 94, 181, 0.08);
  }

  .matters-card h4 {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    color: var(--blue-deep);
    margin-bottom: 0.6rem;
  }

  .matters-card p {
    font-size: 0.88rem;
    color: var(--text-light);
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .matters-card a {
    color: var(--blue);
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  /* Roadmap */
  .roadmap {
    margin-top: 3rem;
    position: relative;
    padding-left: 2rem;
  }

  .roadmap::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    left: 7px;
    top: 0;
    bottom: 0;
    width: 2px;
    background: var(--border);
  }

  .roadmap-item {
    position: relative;
    padding-bottom: 2.5rem;
    padding-left: 2rem;
  }

  .roadmap-item:last-child {
    padding-bottom: 0;
  }

  .roadmap-marker {
    position: absolute;
    left: -2rem;
    top: 0.3rem;
    width: 16px;
    height: 16px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--border);
    border: 3px solid var(--white);
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .roadmap-item.active .roadmap-marker {
    background: var(--gold);
    box-shadow: 0 0 0 4px rgba(244, 169, 48, 0.2);
  }

  .roadmap-phase {
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--teal);
    margin-bottom: 0.3rem;
  }

  .roadmap-content h4 {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-size: 1.15rem;
    color: var(--blue-deep);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .roadmap-content p {
    font-size: 0.88rem;
    color: var(--text-light);
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .layers-grid,
    .matters-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>
